'''Tutlayin timaziɣin n waṭlas''' gant yat tawja n [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] n ugafa. Tutlayin ad llan ɣ [[Idrarn n Waṭlas|idrarn n waṭlas]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]]. 

Iɣ nsawl f tmaziɣt n waṭlas ad st ur tsmrkasm d [[Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas anammas|tmaziɣt n waṭlas anammas]]; tamaziɣt n waṭlas tamu gis ula [[Taclḥit|tclḥit]] d tmaziɣt n Usammer. Ittuga-as yism ad acku tlla ɣ [[Idrarn n Waṭlas|idrarn n waṭlas]] s kraḍ; [[Aṭlas anammas|anammas]] d way [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|mẓẓiyn]] d way [[Aṭlas mqqurn|mqqurn]] d izuɣar d tnzrufin illan gratsn d tama nnsn.

Tamaziɣt n waṭlas tga yan yiẓli zɣ tutlayt [[tamaziɣt n ugafa]], d rad tg yat zɣ trsal n tmaziɣt ad. Tamaziɣt n waṭlas tumẓ zɣ [[Ṣfru]] ɣ ugafa ar [[Glmim]] ɣ unẓul, s ɣmka, tumẓ yat tjumma tasknakalt imqqurn d da sis isawal yan wuṭṭun imqqurn n imaziɣn, ar t-nttḍkaḍ s wattayn n 10 n imlyunen<ref>[[ethnologue:shi/24|Tachelhit | Ethnologue]]</ref><ref>[[ethnologue:tzm/24|Tamazight, Central Atlas | Ethnologue]]</ref>.

Tutlayin timaziɣin n waṭlas gant<ref name="Kossman">-{[[Maarten Kossmann]], "[https://www.academia.edu/8902056/Berber_subclassification_preliminary_version_ Berber subclassification (preliminary version)]", Leiden (2011)}-</ref>:

* [[Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas anammas|Tamaziɣt n waṭlas anammas]], tlla-nn ɣ idrarn n [[Aṭlas anammas|waṭlas anammas]].
* [[Taclḥit]], tlla-nn ɣ iffus n [[Lmɣrib]].
* [[Taznagt n Srayer]], tlla-nn taman [[Rrif]] ɣ iffus nns.
* [[Taɣumarit]], tlla-nn ɣ ugafa n [[Jbala]].
*[[Ils Aɣarbi|Ɣarbi]], awal ad immut, ikka-tt-inn ɣ [[Tamsna]], tasga lli mu tinin ɣila [[Tigmmi Tumlilt|Tigmmi tumlilt]] d [[Rrbaṭ|Rrbat]] d nawaḥi nnsn.
